#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:4
msgid "SCQL Compiler Configuration"
msgstr "SCQL 编译器配置"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:6
msgid ""
"The SCQL compiler translates SQL queries into secure execution plans. "
"This document describes the configuration options for the compiler API."
msgstr "SCQL 编译器将 SQL 查询转换为安全执行计划。本文档描述编译器 API 的配置选项。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:10
msgid "CompileSQLRequest"
msgstr "CompileSQLRequest 编译请求"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:12
msgid "The main request message for compiling SQL queries."
msgstr "编译 SQL 查询的主要请求消息。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:14
msgid "**query** (*required*): The SQL query string to compile"
msgstr "**query** （*必需*）：要编译的 SQL 查询字符串"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:15
msgid "**db** (*optional*): Database name"
msgstr "**db** （*可选*）：数据库名称"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:16
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**issuer** (*required*): The party code of the query issuer (e.g., "
"``{\"code\": \"alice\"}``)"
msgstr "**issuer** （*必需*）：查询发起方的参与方代码（例如， ``{\"code\": \"alice\"}`` ）"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:17
msgid ""
"**catalog** (*required*): Database catalog metadata describing tables and"
" columns, see :ref:`catalog_config`"
msgstr "**catalog** （*必需*）：描述表和列的数据库目录元数据，参见 :ref:`catalog_config`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:18
msgid ""
"**compile_opts** (*required*): Compilation options, see "
":ref:`compile_options`"
msgstr "**compile_opts** （*必需*）：编译选项，参见 :ref:`compile_options`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:19
msgid ""
"**issue_time** (*required*): Query issue timestamp, used for functions "
"like ``NOW()``"
msgstr "**issue_time** （*必需*）：查询发起时间戳，用于 ``NOW()`` 等函数"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:20
msgid ""
"**security_config** (*required*): Security configuration, see "
":ref:`security_config`"
msgstr "**security_config** （*必需*）：安全配置，参见 :ref:`security_config`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:21
msgid ""
"**additional_info** (*required*): Specifies additional information in "
"response, see :ref:`additional_info_spec`"
msgstr "**additional_info** （*必需*）：指定响应中的附加信息，参见 :ref:`additional_info_spec`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:27
msgid "CompileOptions"
msgstr "CompileOptions 编译选项"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:29
msgid "Compilation options that control the execution strategy."
msgstr "控制执行策略的编译选项。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:31
msgid ""
"**spu_conf** (*required*): SPU runtime configuration (protocol, field, "
"etc.), see `SPU documentation`_"
msgstr "**spu_conf** （*必需*）：SPU 运行时配置（协议、域等），参见 `SPU documentation`_"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:32
msgid "**batched** (*required*): Whether to run in streaming mode"
msgstr "**batched** （*必需*）：是否以流式模式运行"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:33
msgid ""
"**psi_algorithm_type** (*optional*): PSI algorithm type: ``UNSPECIFIED`` "
"(auto), ``ECDH_PSI``, ``KKRT_PSI``, ``RR22``"
msgstr ""
"**psi_algorithm_type** （*可选*）：PSI 算法类型： ``UNSPECIFIED`` （自动）、 "
"``ECDH_PSI`` 、 ``KKRT_PSI`` 、 ``RR22``"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:35
msgid "**SPU Configuration Example:**"
msgstr "**SPU 配置示例：**"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:47
msgid "**Supported SPU Protocols:**"
msgstr "**支持的 SPU 协议：**"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:49
msgid "``SEMI2K``: Semi-honest 2PC/MPC (supports N parties)"
msgstr "``SEMI2K`` ：半诚实 2PC/MPC（支持 N 方）"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:50
msgid "``CHEETAH``: Semi-honest 2PC (2 parties only)"
msgstr "``CHEETAH`` ：半诚实 2PC（仅支持 2 方）"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:51
msgid "``ABY3``: Semi-honest 3PC (3 parties only)"
msgstr "``ABY3`` ：半诚实 3PC（仅支持 3 方）"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:53
msgid "**Supported Fields:**"
msgstr "**支持的域：**"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:55
msgid "``FM32``: 32-bit finite field"
msgstr "``FM32`` ：32 位有限域"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:56
msgid "``FM64``: 64-bit finite field"
msgstr "``FM64`` ：64 位有限域"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:57
msgid "``FM128``: 128-bit finite field"
msgstr "``FM128`` ：128 位有限域"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:63
msgid "CompilerSecurityConfig"
msgstr "CompilerSecurityConfig 安全配置"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:65
msgid ""
"Security configuration that controls data visibility and security "
"relaxations."
msgstr "控制数据可见性和安全放宽的安全配置。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:67
msgid ""
"**global_relaxation** (*required*): Global security relaxation settings, "
"see :ref:`global_security_relaxation`"
msgstr ""
"**global_relaxation** （*必需*）：全局安全放宽设置，参见 "
":ref:`global_security_relaxation`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:68
msgid ""
"**column_relaxation_list** (*optional*): Per-column security relaxations,"
" see :ref:`column_security_relaxation`"
msgstr ""
"**column_relaxation_list** （*可选*）：按列的安全放宽设置，参见 "
":ref:`column_security_relaxation`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:69
msgid ""
"**reverse_inference_conf** (*required*): Reverse inference detection "
"config, see :ref:`reverse_inference_config`"
msgstr ""
"**reverse_inference_conf** （*必需*）：反向推理检测配置，参见 "
":ref:`reverse_inference_config`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:70
msgid ""
"**column_visibility_list** (*optional*): User-specified column "
"visibility, see :ref:`column_visibility`"
msgstr "**column_visibility_list** （*可选*）：用户指定的列可见性，参见 :ref:`column_visibility`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:71
msgid ""
"**result_security_conf** (*optional*): Result-level security config, see "
":ref:`result_security_config`"
msgstr "**result_security_conf** （*可选*）：结果级安全配置，参见 :ref:`result_security_config`"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:77
msgid "GlobalSecurityRelaxation"
msgstr "全局安全放松"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:79
msgid "Global security relaxation that applies to all data."
msgstr "适用于所有数据的全局安全放松配置。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:81
msgid ""
"**reveal_group_count** (*optional*): Allow group counts to be visible in "
"plaintext"
msgstr "**reveal_group_count** （*可选*）：允许分组计数以明文可见"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:82
msgid ""
"**reveal_group_mark** (*optional*): Allow group marks to be visible in "
"plaintext"
msgstr "**reveal_group_mark** （*可选*）：允许分组标记以明文可见"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:83
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:110
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**reveal_key_after_join** (*optional*): Allow join keys to be visible in "
"plaintext after join (intersection only). When enabled, the compiler will"
" prefer PSI join over secret join for better performance"
msgstr ""
"**reveal_key_after_join** （*可选*）：允许连接键明文可见。启用后，编译器将优先选择 "
"PSI join 而非 secret join，以获得更好的性能"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:84
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:111
msgid ""
"**reveal_filter_mask** (*optional*): Allow filter mask to be used in "
"plaintext for subsequent computations"
msgstr "**reveal_filter_mask** （*可选*）：允许过滤掩码可以在后续计算中当作明文使用"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:86
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:116
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:143
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:168
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:197
msgid "**Example:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:103
msgid "ColumnSecurityRelaxation"
msgstr "列级安全放松"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:105
msgid "Per-column security relaxation for fine-grained control."
msgstr "用于细粒度控制的列级安全放松配置。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:107
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:161
msgid "**database** (*required*): Database name"
msgstr "**database** （*必需*）：数据库名称"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:108
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:162
msgid "**table** (*required*): Table name"
msgstr "**table** （*必需*）：表名称"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:109
#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:163
msgid "**column** (*required*): Column name"
msgstr "**column** （*必需*）：列名称"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:114
msgid ""
"Column-level settings use logical OR with global settings. If global "
"``reveal_key_after_join`` is ``true`` and column-level is ``false``, the "
"result is ``true``. If global is ``false`` and column-level is ``true``, "
"the result is ``true``. Only when both are ``false`` is the final result "
"``false``. The same logic applies to ``reveal_filter_mask``."
msgstr ""
"列级设置与全局设置使用逻辑或运算。如果全局 ``reveal_key_after_join`` 为 ``true`` 而列级为 "
"``false`` ，结果为 ``true`` 。如果全局为 ``false`` 而列级为 ``true`` ，结果为 ``true`` 。"
"只有当两者都为 ``false`` 时，最终结果才为 ``false`` 。 ``reveal_filter_mask`` 也适用相同的逻辑。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:135
msgid "ReverseInferenceConfig"
msgstr "结果反推配置"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:137
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuration for reverse inference."
msgstr "用于结果反推的配置。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:139
msgid ""
"**enable_reverse_inference** (*required*): Infer intermediate visibility "
"from result visibility to enable plaintext compute"
msgstr "**enable_reverse_inference** （*必需*）：从结果可见性推断中间可见性以启用明文计算"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:141
msgid ""
"When enabled, the compiler will infer the visibility of intermediate "
"computation steps based on the final result visibility, increasing the "
"possibility of plaintext computation and improving performance."
msgstr "启用后，编译器将根据最终结果的可见性推断中间计算步骤的可见性，从而增加明文计算的可能性并提高性能。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:157
msgid "ColumnVisibility"
msgstr "列可见性"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:159
msgid "Specifies which parties can see specific columns."
msgstr "指定哪些参与方可以查看特定列。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:164
msgid ""
"**visible_parties** (*required*): List of party codes that can see this "
"column during computation (in addition to the owner)"
msgstr "**visible_parties** （*必需*）：可在计算期间查看该列的参与方代码列表（除所有者之外）"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:166
msgid ""
"By default, only the column owner can see the data. Use this to grant "
"visibility to other parties. Adding column visibility will make the "
"execution graph prefer plaintext operators, improving execution "
"efficiency."
msgstr "默认情况下，只有列所有者可以查看数据。使用此配置可以向其他参与方授予可见性。增加列可见性会使执行图更优先使用明文算子，提高执行效率。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:189
msgid "ResultSecurityConfig"
msgstr "结果安全配置"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:191
msgid "Security configuration that affects query results."
msgstr "影响查询结果的安全配置。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:193
msgid ""
"**groupby_threshold** (*optional*): Minimum number of rows in a group for"
" GROUP BY results (default: 4)"
msgstr "**groupby_threshold** （*可选*）：GROUP BY 结果中一个分组的最小行数（默认值：4）"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:195
msgid ""
"Groups with fewer rows than this threshold will be filtered out to "
"prevent inference attacks."
msgstr "行数少于此阈值的分组将被过滤掉，以防止推理攻击。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:211
msgid "AdditionalInfoSpec"
msgstr "附加信息规范"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:213
msgid "Specifies what additional information should be included in the response."
msgstr "指定应在响应中包含哪些附加信息。"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:215
msgid ""
"**need_operator_graph** (*optional*): Whether to return the operator "
"graph for debugging (default: ``false``)"
msgstr "**need_operator_graph** （*可选*）：是否返回用于调试的算子图（默认值： ``false`` ）"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:221
msgid "Catalog Configuration"
msgstr "数据目录配置"

#: ../../reference/compiler-config.rst:223
